{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778378557726,"sessionID":"ses_1f062fb4cffeIXH4xhAItXOUHt","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_NrtQvpPgTScNAcoZ3gp0FcoB","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Definitions for insular cortex and Brodmann (1909) area 9 have been added and committed locally for PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+Added definitions for the two previously undefined terms requested in issue #3448:\n+\n+- `UBERON:0034891` insular cortex\n+- `UBERON:0013540` Brodmann (1909) area 9\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The definitions were adapted from the issue-provided source material while keeping them concise and anatomy-focused. The insular cortex definition mirrors the existing logical placement as a cortex of cerebral lobe that is part of the insula. The Brodmann area 9 definition reflects its existing placement under Brodmann area and summarizes the source-provided cytoarchitectural characterization.\n+\n+Both updated terms were linked back to issue #3448 using `term_tracker_item`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the current stanzas for both requested UBERON terms.\n+- Checked parent/part-of context for consistency.\n+- Verified the MeSH descriptor for insular cortex as `MESH:D000087623` using the MeSH Browser.\n+- Checked the referenced Wikipedia source pages for both terms.\n+- Edited checked-out term stanzas and checked them back into `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+- Reserialized the ontology with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated OBO conversion with `robot convert` to a temporary output.\n+- Ran `git diff --check`.\n+- Committed only `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` locally.\n+\n+Signed-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+Definitions for insular cortex and Brodmann (1909) area 9 have been added and committed locally for PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,27 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+Added definitions for the two previously undefined terms requested in issue #3448:\n+\n+- `UBERON:0034891` insular cortex\n+- `UBERON:0013540` Brodmann (1909) area 9\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The definitions were adapted from the issue-provided source material while keeping them concise and anatomy-focused. The insular cortex definition mirrors the existing logical placement as a cortex of cerebral lobe that is part of the insula. The Brodmann area 9 definition reflects its existing placement under Brodmann area and summarizes the source-provided cytoarchitectural characterization.\n+\n+Both updated terms were linked back to issue #3448 using `term_tracker_item`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the current stanzas for both requested UBERON terms.\n+- Checked parent/part-of context for consistency.\n+- Verified the MeSH descriptor for insular cortex as `MESH:D000087623` using the MeSH Browser.\n+- Checked the referenced Wikipedia source pages for both terms.\n+- Edited checked-out term stanzas and checked them back into `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+- Reserialized the ontology with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated OBO conversion with `robot convert` to a temporary output.\n+- Ran `git diff --check`.\n+- Committed only `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` locally.\n+\n+Signed-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+Definitions for insular cortex and Brodmann (1909) area 9 have been added and committed locally for PR #<NN>.\n","additions":1,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,27 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+Added definitions for the two previously undefined terms requested in issue #3448:\n+\n+- `UBERON:0034891` insular cortex\n+- `UBERON:0013540` Brodmann (1909) area 9\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The definitions were adapted from the issue-provided source material while keeping them concise and anatomy-focused. The insular cortex definition mirrors the existing logical placement as a cortex of cerebral lobe that is part of the insula. The Brodmann area 9 definition reflects its existing placement under Brodmann area and summarizes the source-provided cytoarchitectural characterization.\n+\n+Both updated terms were linked back to issue #3448 using `term_tracker_item`.\n+\n+## Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the current stanzas for both requested UBERON terms.\n+- Checked parent/part-of context for consistency.\n+- Verified the MeSH descriptor for insular cortex as `MESH:D000087623` using the MeSH Browser.\n+- Checked the referenced Wikipedia source pages for both terms.\n+- Edited checked-out term stanzas and checked them back into `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n+- Reserialized the ontology with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated OBO conversion with `robot convert` to a temporary output.\n+- Ran `git diff --check`.\n+- Committed only `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` locally.\n+\n+Signed-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\n","additions":27,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778378557718,"end":1778378557724}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02cb225e42721f110169ffe73917748190a665831be87adf06"}},"id":"prt_e0f9f37240010l4U8Mif3jIOxw","sessionID":"ses_1f062fb4cffeIXH4xhAItXOUHt","messageID":"msg_e0f9f2bdd001eMFKXTtjNaxP82"}}
